data.title: PRG Real Estate wins 2026 Grace Hill Elite 5 Award for fifth year, ranked #4 in Tier 2 category.
data.description: In Philadelphia on February 27, 2026, PRG Real Estate received accolades for exceptional resident satisfaction. The company was honored with the 2026 Grace Hill Elite 5 Award for the fifth year in a row, achieving the #4 spot in the Tier 2 category. This recognition signifies PRG Real Estate's continuous commitment to excellence in providing top-notch residential experiences.
